Most Rekichū are based on the principles of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行説|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}} and the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} and {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} ({{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}). Generally, calendars list scientific and astronomical details such as dates, {{ill|days of the week|ja|曜日|1=Day of the week|2=ja|3=曜日|qq=|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/days of the week|13=User:Immanuelle/Day of the week|qq=}}, {{ill|solar terms|ja|二十四節気|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/solar terms|qq=}}, and {{ill|72 pentads|ja|七十二候|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/72 pentads|qq=}} in the top section. The middle section typically features {{ill|Jūni choku|ja|十二直|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jūni choku|qq=}}, while the lower section contains items like {{ill|Sembi|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sembi|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}}, {{ill|28 mansions|ja|二十八宿|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/28 mansions|qq=}}, {{ill|Nine Star Ki|ja|九星|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nine Star Ki|qq=}}, and {{ill|Rekichū Gedan|ja|暦注下段|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rekichū Gedan|qq=}}. 
